text: "Bulletproof" is a 2009 song by the English electropop duo La Roux off their self-titled album. It was released in the United Kingdom in June 2009 and was highly received by the critics. This song debuted at #1 on the UK Singles Chart. It was a sleeper hit in the United States, peaking at number eight. Category:2009 songs Category:Synth-pop
title: Bulletproof (La Roux song)
